author: ashish
msg: AddItemRequest in ebay code was not allowing export of more then one item to ebay.

In the request you can send the single item at a time and if you wanted to exported more then one item then you may need to call the same request multiple times.For more details please refer link shown below.
-- After this commit you can either export one item or more then one item from OFBiz to eBay (OFBiz --> eBay).
-- Moved while loop in the main method so you will also see formating changes.
